(match let rec search lo hi =
        assert (lo < hi);
        assert (((get arr lo) < key) && (key < (get arr hi)));
        if (lo + 1) = hi
        then Some hi
        else
          (let mid = (lo + hi) / 2 in
           match Stdlib.compare key (get arr mid) with
           | 0 -> Some mid
           | c when c < 0 -> search lo mid
           | _ -> search mid hi) in
      search lo hi
with
| None -> _
| Some _ -> _)

      then (stats, missing_hash)
      else
        (let (buffer_off, off, missing_hash) =
           match decode_entry_exn ~off
                   ~buffer:(Bytes.unsafe_to_string (!buffer)) ~buffer_off
           with
           | { key; data } ->
               let (off', entry_len, kind) = data in
               let entry_lenL = Int63.of_int entry_len in
               (assert (off = off');
                Stats.add stats kind;
                progress entry_lenL;
                (let off = let open Int63.Syntax in off + entry_lenL in
                 let missing_hash =
                   on_entry { data; key } stats iter_pack_entry missing_hash in
                 ((buffer_off + entry_len), off, missing_hash)))
           | exception Not_enough_buffer ->
               (match if buffer_off > 0
                      then refill_buffer ~from:off
                      else expand_and_refill_buffer ~from:off
                with
                | () -> (0, off, missing_hash)) in
         loop_entries ~buffer_off off missing_hash)
with
| (_, _) -> _

with

| Error _ -> _

(match let (new_suffix_start_offset, latest_gc_target_offset) =
        let ((_ as state) : _ Pack_key.state) =
          (Pack_key.inspect commit_key : _ Pack_key.state) in
        match state with
        | Direct x ->
            let len = Int63.of_int x.length in
            ((let open Int63.Syntax in x.offset + len), (x.offset))
        | Indexed _ -> assert false in
      let status =
        (Fm.Control.payload (Fm.control fm)) |> (fun p -> p.status) in
      let* () =
        match (output, status) with
        | (`Root, Gced previous) when
            let open Int63.Syntax in
              previous.latest_gc_target_offset >= latest_gc_target_offset
            ->
            Error
              (`Gc_disallowed
                 (Fmt.str
                    (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Format
                       ((CamlinternalFormatBasics.Alpha
                           (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                              (" is less than or equal to previous GC offset of ",
                                (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Alpha
                                   CamlinternalFormatBasics.End_of_format)))),
                         "%a is less than or equal to previous GC offset of %a"))
                    Int63.pp latest_gc_target_offset Int63.pp
                    previous.latest_gc_target_offset))
        | _ -> Ok ()
       in
      let new_files_path =
        match output with | `Root -> root | `External path -> path in
      let new_suffix_start_offset =
        match status with
        | Gced { suffix_start_offset;_} when
            let open Int63.Syntax in
              suffix_start_offset >= latest_gc_target_offset
            -> suffix_start_offset
        | _ -> new_suffix_start_offset in
      let partial_stats =
        let commit_offset = latest_gc_target_offset in
        let before_suffix_start_offset =
          Dispatcher.suffix_start_offset dispatcher in
        let before_suffix_end_offset = Dispatcher.end_offset dispatcher in
        Gc_stats.Main.create "worker startup" ~generation ~commit_offset
          ~before_suffix_start_offset ~before_suffix_end_offset
          ~after_suffix_start_offset:new_suffix_start_offset in
      let unlink_result_file () =
        let result_file = Irmin_pack.Layout.V4.gc_result ~generation ~root in
        match Io.classify_path result_file with
        | `File ->
            Io.unlink_dont_wait
              ~on_exn:(fun exn ->
                         Log.warn
                           (fun f ->
                              f ?header:None
                                ?tags:(Some
                                         (Logs.Tag.add
                                            Ppx_irmin_internal_lib.Source_code_position.tag
                                            __POS__ Logs.Tag.empty))
                                (CamlinternalFormatBasics.Format
                                   ((CamlinternalFormatBasics.String_literal
                                       ("Unlinking temporary files from previous failed gc. Failed with error ",
                                         (CamlinternalFormatBasics.String
                                            (CamlinternalFormatBasics.No_padding,
                                              CamlinternalFormatBasics.End_of_format)))),
                                     "Unlinking temporary files from previous failed gc. Failed with error %s"))
                                (Printexc.to_string exn))) result_file
        | `Directory | `No_such_file_or_directory | `Other -> () in
      unlink_result_file ();
      (let (promise, resolver) = Lwt.wait () in
       let task =
         Async.async
           (fun () ->
              Worker.run_and_output_result ~lower_root ~generation
                ~new_files_path root commit_key new_suffix_start_offset) in
       let partial_stats =
         Gc_stats.Main.finish_current_step partial_stats "before finalise" in
       Ok
         {
           latest_gc_target_offset;
           resulting_stats = None;
           partial_stats;
           commit;
           node;
           contents;
           fm;
           dispatcher;
           promise;
           resolver;
           new_suffix_start_offset;
           unlink;
           task;
           generation;
           root
         })
with
| Ok _ -> _
| Error _ -> _)

value:
match let create_chunk i =
        let suffix_off = !off_acc in
        let is_appendable = i = (chunk_num - 1) in
        let chunk_idx = start_idx + i in
        let is_legacy = is_legacy chunk_idx in
        let open_result = open_chunk ~chunk_idx ~is_legacy ~is_appendable in
        match open_result with
        | Error err -> raise (OpenInventoryError err)
        | Ok ao ->
            (off_acc := (end_offset_of_chunk suffix_off ao);
             { ao; suffix_off; idx = chunk_idx }) in
      try Ok (v chunk_num create_chunk)
      with
      | OpenInventoryError err -> Error (err : open_error  :> [> open_error])
with
| Ok _ -> _
| Error _ -> _
